fix: agent called complete_task with literal string 'TASK_ID' instead of the actual UUID because the prompt never included the task ID. The agent had no way to know its own task ID. Fixed by adding 'Task ID: {uuid}' to the initial prompt header and including the specific ID in all tool call instructions (complete_task, create_task, continuation prompt). This was the root cause of the infinite loop — the complete_task call silently failed because 'TASK_ID' didn't match any task.
